data.description: Come check out this beautiful home right in the heart of Tucson Estates; where you own the land! This affixed mobile home has double masters with a split bedroom floor plan. Plenty of windows, and a skylight in the master bath fill this house with light. The kitchen is full of color, has a gas range and cabinets have extra built in drawers. Enjoy the mountain views from the sunroom or back patio. There is an additional deck out front with an extra storage shed and a cement paved carport.  Never a dull moment in this community,  it has a full 18 hole golf course, great hiking trails, a pool, sauna, tennis courts, library, rec room and more!
